'''''The Admiral's List''''' was an official publication of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]] during the [[Mandalorian Wars]], covering news related to the war effort from the Navy's viewpoint.

==Issues==
*{{KOTORbackups|13}}
*{{KOTORbackups|16}}
*{{KOTORbackups|22}}

==Behind the scenes==
''The Admiral's List'' is one of a number of "news organs" based on the ''[[Taris Holofeed]]'' that are included as extras in monthly issues of [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic (comic series)|''Knights of the Old Republic'']] starting with [[Knights of the Old Republic 13|issue 13]].

